org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.write.chunk

Class ChunkWriterImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iotdb.tsfile.write.chunk.ChunkWriterImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IChunkWriter

    public class ChunkWriterImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IChunkWriter
    A implementation of IChunkWriter. ChunkWriterImpl consists of a ChunkBuffer, a PageWriter, and two Statistics.
